{
 "name": "RPlog_Selene_Day_Space_Race",
 "title": "Selene Day Space Race",
 "summary": "The first Selene Day Race pits three starfighter pilots against a gauntlet of obstacles over the Imperial capital, with Grand Admiral Danik Kreldin watching from his Super Star Destroyer. The Imperial War Shrike officer Krieg Inrokana, the veteran Corellian pilot Tyler Damion racing under the alias Anders Kain, and the civilian Talia Andorn blast through an artificial asteroid field, a low-power mine field, the gutted hull of a Star Destroyer, a mock space battle, and finally a recreation of the Death Star's reactor shaft. Tyler and Talia trade the lead while the cautious Krieg uses them to read the course, until his TIE's stabilizers tear off at ludicrous speed inside the Death Star, knocking him unconscious and out of the race. A simulated fireball chases the survivors out of the structure, and Tyler streaks ahead toward the finish line at the Malevolence with Talia close behind.",
